title: How should we split the UNIC rewards for uJENNY LPs?
body:
It looks like the proposal on Unicly to allow collections to split UNIC rewards between uJENNY-ETH and uJENNY-UNIC liquidity providers will pass.

Read more: https://snapshot.org/#/uniclynft.eth/proposal/QmWEPVkHcjAP2SMM6wqbDP3ZFG79AGmnVcVMzoAJSsFnn3

What should the split be for uJENNY LPs?
1. 0% uJENNY-UNIC, 100% uJENNY-ETH
2. 25% uJENNY-UNIC, 75% uJENNY-ETH
3. 50% uJENNY-UNIC, 50% uJENNY-ETH
4. 75% uJENNY-UNIC, 25% uJENNY-ETH
5. 100% uJENNY-UNIC, 0% uJENNY-ETH
author: 0x0eF024d299cb56805F2437Cd00b8A361a7B06D54
